          "url": "https://wikem.org/wiki/Hypotension"
        }
      ]
    },
    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Elevated\nAG metabolic acidosis\nHypotension\nBradycardia\nRhabdomyolysis\nHyperkalemia\nAKI\nHyperlipidemia\nTransaminitis, fatty liver",
