    "Management": {
      "text": "Immediate discontinuation of propofol infusion\nTreatment of\nrhabdomyolysis\n, to include renal replacement therapy\nHemodynamic support, cardiac\npacing\nL-carnitine\nsupplementation\nCarbohydrate administration at 6-8mg/kg/min\nHemodialysis\nECMO\nin refractory cases",
